pfsrd://Game Mastery Guide/Rules/Sanity and Madness/Types of Insanity/Schizophrenia
pfsrd://Game Mastery Guide/Rules/Sanity and Madness/Types of Insanity/Schizophrenia/Description A schizophrenic character has lost his grip on reality/and can no longer tell the difference between what is real and what is not. These constant hallucinations cause the schizophrenic to appear erratic/chaotic/and unpredictable to others. Each time a schizophrenic character finds himself in a stressful situation he must make a Will save against his insanitys DC. Failure indicates that the character becomes confused for 1d6 rounds.
